page.title: 13Ecology_Wildlife
page.content: There are lots of animals in this area.Foxes are very common.There are lots of wild flowers in this area. Daisies and dandelions are very popular. Daisies have little white petals joined on to a mustardy yellow coloured centre.Rabbits are plentiful.Also there are lots of different kinds of grass.One kind of grass has heads that make it look like corn,but most of the grass is ordinary.Danddelions have yellow petals.Rabbits are also kept as pets,There are also lots of other popular animals and floers and plants in the area around Dorset .
